Package com.atlan.model.assets

Class IndistinctAsset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atlan.model.core.AtlanObject
      • com.atlan.model.relations.Reference
        • com.atlan.model.assets.Asset
          • com.atlan.model.assets.IndistinctAsset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAsset, IReferenceable, AuditDetail, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Reference>
    public class IndistinctAsset
extends Asset
    Instance of an asset where we cannot determine (have not yet modeled) its detailed information. In the meanwhile, this provides a catch-all case where at least the basic asset information is available.
